{"tid":2190921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「蘇9」致電基亞連尼：唔好介意咬過你","createTime":"2020-09-06T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T07:42:15.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6b903dd6a587f3174d571b57cdb6f749fc6f75","tid":2190921,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"　　巴塞球星蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez）給祖記後衛基亞連尼（Giorgio Chiellini）打了電話，就當年的「咬人事件」進行和解。<br />\n<br />\n　　在2014年巴西世界盃烏拉圭與意大利的比賽中，蘇亞雷斯咬了基亞連尼的肩膀，當時逃過了球證的處罰，不過，他在後來被追加處罰停賽四個月。<br />\n<br />\n　　據《米蘭體育報》稱，如今蘇亞雷斯有望加盟祖雲達斯，他於是給祖記隊長基亞連尼打了電話，試圖化解當年風波，拉近兩人的關係。<br />\n<br />\n　　其實基亞連尼在事後並未記仇，他曾在採訪中說：「這是他在近身搏鬥中的招數，我也有這類招數，他和我有點相似。」而蘇亞雷斯當年也曾承認：「我錯了，但我也是人，會有衝動的時候。」"},{"pid":"4dc08dc93a144fc24d98f1a7285984e0f452cc40","tid":2190921,"uid":136416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"然後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更衣室互咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb69418c122373f5090f396482a418772e5187a","tid":2190921,"uid":120965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4dc08dc93a144fc24d98f1a7285984e0f452cc40","tid":2190921,"uid":136416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"然後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更衣室互咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2af7b54ba9cdd5fc2937f6386d988ea2e00577","tid":2190921,"uid":204126,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}